Zayn Malik | Image: Grammy In anticipation of his forthcoming album, British singer and songwriter Zayn Malik has shared a new song “Vibez”. The former One Direction member released “Vibez” on Thursday night, as he unveiled the album art for his upcoming third studio album “Nobody Is Listening” which he announced is due out on January 15. “Vibez” is the second single off the new album. Malik, 27, previously released the album’s lead single “Better” back in September. Listen to “Vibez” below: In an interview with Entertainment Daily, Malik described the “Nobody Is Listening”  as his “most personal project to date”.